{"ts":"2026-06-27T03:03:11.902Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Designing Mobile Navigation**\n\nI'm now focusing on a highly responsive mobile navigation design. I've decided on a bottom navigation bar, visible only on smaller screens, that includes actions for Dashboard, Projects, AI Operations, Support/Docs, and a \"More\" option to open a drawer with full access. I'm prioritizing clear active states with blue highlights for the bottom navigation icons. The goal is rapid access to core functions on mobile, with a comprehensive drawer for full access.\n\n\n","redacted":false}}
